---
import ProjectOptions from "./ProjectOptions.astro";
---

<section id="todo" class="col-span-5 row-span-3 rounded-md">
  <div id="todo-content">
    <p>
      Proyecto que representa el tipico todo list construido con react y consumo
      de servicio externo para manejo del mismo
    </p>
    <ProjectOptions
      hrefGit="https://github.com/GuarU345/todo-list.git"
      hrefWeb="https://guaru345todo-list.netlify.app"
    />
  </div>
</section>
<section id="spotify" class="col-span-7 row-span-4 rounded-md">
  <div id="spotify-content">
    <p>
      Clon de spotify donde podras reproducir musica a tu gusto y ademas
      interactuar con los albums guardandolos en tu biblioteca y crear las
      playlists que desees donde podras guardar tu musica favorita
    </p>
    <ProjectOptions
      hrefGit="https://github.com/GuarU345/spotify-clone-react-ts.git"
      hrefWeb=""
    />
  </div>
</section>
<section id="pokedex" class="col-span-5 p-6 row-span-3 rounded-md">
  <div id="pokedex-content">
    <p>
      Peque√±a pokedex donde podras observar a los pokemones de la primera
      generacion incluye un buscador en el cual podras buscar a tu pokemon
      favorito
    </p>
    <ProjectOptions
      hrefGit="https://github.com/GuarU345/pokedex_react.git"
      hrefWeb="https://pokedex-guaru345.netlify.app"
    />
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #todo {
    position: relative;
    background-image: url("todo-list.png");
    background-size: cover;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    transition: opacity;
  }

  #todo-content {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 16px;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-wrap: pretty;
    @apply bg-gradient-to-tr from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 rounded-md;
  }

  #todo:hover {
    background-image: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    #todo-content {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }
